      About this item

      • 900J Surge Protector Outlet: Featuring a power strip with surge protection, overload protection, short circuit protection offers a comprehensive safeguard for electronics; The switch shuts off automatically during overloads to protect devices
      • 7 in 1 Flat Power Strip: Extension cord with multiple outlets can be expanded to 4 AC Outlets (1250W Max), 1 USB C and 2 USB A; Surge protector power strip with flat head extension cord 5FT can charge 7 devices at the same time, reducing waiting time
      • USB C 15W Charging: USB A ports feature 2.4A max, the USB C port feature 3A max; This flat outlet extender includes 3 USB ports to meet your multiport charging needs; Applicable to cell phone, tablet, earphones, etc
      • 5Ft Flat Extension Cord: With only 0.31 inch flat Plug head design, flat Wall Plug can easily fit in tight spots and hide behind sofa, bed, nightstand or other furniture indoor; 45 degree right angle design create an extra space for other plug below without blocking
      • Mountable Wall Outlet Extender: Featuring 2 wall mount holes for easy space management, this flat power strip offers versatile installation options on workbenches, walls, under counters, etc; 4 rubber feet keep it securely in place, preventing slips and slides

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
